The choice of source for ingredients used in vitamin gummies is becoming a crucial factor for consumers, with the preference shifting towards plant-based options due to the rising demand for vegan and vegetarian-friendly products. Plant-based gummies are gaining traction as more consumers align their purchasing decisions with sustainable and ethical practices. This trend reflects a broader shift towards environmentally conscious consumption patterns, with plant-based vitamin gummies positioned to capture a significant market share in the coming years.

